Muradin,Mountain King Nuker-DSP Starting stats 1 Int, 4 Agi, 6 Str, base speed 280, base damage 5, Stats Gain per level 1.00 int, 1.60 str, 0.00 agi, starting item Rusty Hammer increase damage by 4 and reduce coldown by 4% base attack time 2.10

Stats of the game --- 0.20 damage primary stats --- int give 10 mana --- 10 int will give 1% mana --- 10 int will 1% spell amp --- agi give 1 attack speed --- 10 agi will give 1% bonus damage --- str will give 5 life --- 10 str will give 1% life

