LEVEL 20 TALENT

talent 1
210 life 2.5 life regen and 12% magic resist

talent 2
12 damage 6% spellamp and 12 attack speed


PASSIVE D OR F
Dwarft Might
increase overall stats and give a positive and negative buff

BUFF Muradin Start with 1 armor and any armor lost will be bonus armor for muradin instead of losing it he also gain 1 damage per armor
and 50% of his armor will be Strenght and muradin spell will do 10% bonus pure damage
DEBUFF Muradin lose 15% magic resist and he take 50% more damage from pure and magic resist any magic resist lost takent will be double
instead of normal he also can only use hammer type weapons

Talent level 25 Upgrade Dwarft Might
add a new modifier infused Hammer
every basic attack, Muradin Release a Chain Lightning dealing 4 physical damage plus 10% of strenght and 5% of attack damage
that jump up to 4 target


SPELL Q
Storm Bolt
deal Heavy damage to a target stunning them and reducing magic resist and armor also pushing the target back

damage 10 25 40 55 plus 40% of strenght -damage type MAGICAL-
bonus damage 10% pure
push force 200
magic resist lost 9% 11% 13% 15%
armor lost 1 2 3 4
stun duration 2 3 4 5 last half on bosses
cooldown 16 15 14 13
mana cost 75 plus 2% 4% 6% 8% of max mana

talent level 10 upgrade Storm Bolt
increase strenght scaling by 40%
increase cast range by 300
increase push force by 100
increase the magic resist lost by 5%
stun duration last full on bosses as well

add a new modifier Violent Bolt
after hiting the target it will send other storm bolt to near enemy in a radius of 350
of the explosion of the first one and dealing 50% of the damage to the other target as well
if there is no one around storm bolt damage change to pure and deal 4% of the target max life
as damage


SPELL W
Thunder Clap
Muradin Smash the ground, dealing damage and slowing attack speed and movement speed. The more enemy hit
by this spell the more damage it deal

damage 9 12 15 18 plus 15% of strenght -damage type PURE-
bonus damage 10% pure
radius 260 270 280 290
radius increase by 1 for every point of strenght
attack speed lost 15 20 25 30
movement speed lost 10% 16% 22% 28%
bonus damage per enemy 1 2 3 4
debuff duration 3 4 5 6
cooldown 11
mana cost 70 110 140 170 plus 1% of max mana

talent level 10 Upgrade Thunder Clap
increase damage by 6
increase strenght scaling by 20%
increase radius by 60
increase bonus damage per enemy by 2

add a new mofidier Hammer of Thunder
when Muradin do Thunder Clap for every enemy hit he will get 2 bonus damage for 5 second
and Thunder Clap deal 2% of the current life of the enemy as bonus damage he also heal for 0.75% of is
max life per enemy hit


